Since we use our own version of haskeline we need to install it from a tarball,
and in order to resolve cabal dependencies correctly, haskeline must be built
using transformers >= 0.4.2.0

INSTALL:
--------

cabal sandbox init
cabal install transformers-0.4.3.0
cabal install haskeline-0.7.1.4.tar.gz
cabal install --only-dependencies

CONFIGURATION:
--------------

cabal configure

or with tests

cabal configure --enable-tests

BUILD:
------

cabal build
